Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:00:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}待在原地\NStay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们在这里干什么\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}丹尼尔  救命\NDaniel, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没做错什么\NI've done nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}托马斯  快跑\NThomas, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别伤害我的孩子们\NDon't you hurt my kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}科尔牧师\NReverend Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是时候了  亨利\NTime's come, Henry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}将奴隶制的罪恶从这片土地上冲走\NFor the sins of slavery to be washed away from this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}由你手上的血来净化  这是上帝的旨意\NPurged by blood from your hands as foreordained by god himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝\NLord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}发发慈悲\NHave mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只要有被奴役的人  我就与他们同在\NFor as long as there are those in bonds, I am bound with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}离开这里\NLeave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们自由了\NYou are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  他们属于我\NNo, they're--they're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有触犯法律\NI have broken no law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}法律\NLaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不承认任何尘世的主人  他们也不该承认\NI acknowledge no master in human form, nor should they.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但如果要我放弃自己的生命\NBut if I be asked to forfeit my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来为他们寻求公正\Nin furtherance of justice for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很乐意让自己的双手\NI will gladly mingle my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}沾上被杀者之血\Nwith that which I spill...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就在今晚\NTonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不要\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}爸爸\NPa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-执行旨意吧  -不要\N- Let it be done! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝\NRuth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你做了什么\NWhat'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她做了很多事\NOh, she did plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能照顾她吗\NWill you tend to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-当然  -带走她\N- Of course. - Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她枪击了一个人\NShe shot a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你就是法律  -我会处理的\N- You're the law. - I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这还不够\NThat's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}教会的女士还真会开枪\NThose church ladies sure can shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭嘴  我需要别人帮我抬他\NShut up. I need help with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他死吧\NLet him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕萨姆  德莱尼  来吧\NPsalms? Delaney? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}扶他起来\NGet him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别管他  他不配活着\NLeave him. He don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他要是死了露丝就是杀人犯了\NHe dies, Ruth's a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把后面那张桌子腾出来\NClear off that back table!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早餐时间结束  各位\NBreakfast is over, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}轻点轻点\NEasy, easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说了轻点\NAhh! I said easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你需要什么  博汉南先生\NWhat you need, Mr. Bohannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有伊娃在\NWe got Eva here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们回去干活吧\NGet on back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}德莱尼  我们需要造好那台蒸汽挖土机\NDelaney? Need that steam shovel built.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕萨姆\NPsalms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}子弹直接穿过去了\NBullet went clear through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这颗还在他体内\NThis one's still in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你不会把手伸进我身体里找子弹\NWell, I know you ain't going fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道个屁\NYou don't know shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他快失血过多了\NHe's bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要是不把子弹取出来  他会死的\NWe don't get that bullet out, he gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要些咖啡渣\NI need some coffee grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有多少拿多少来\NMuch as you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他需要看医生\NHe needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不是在这吗\NWell, he's got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-按住他  -混...啊...\N- Hold him still. - Son of a--ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果不给我找医生  还不如给我找个牧师来\NIf you ain't got a doctor, you might as well find me a priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}严格来说露丝只能算教堂工作人员  此处简翻为牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是牧师开枪打的你\NClosest thing we got put this bullet in ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝给予你生命  然后将之带走\NThe lord giveth and the lord taketh away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝\NRuth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道发生了什么事吗\NDo you know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道这里是什么地方吗\NDo you know where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以斯拉已经入土...\NEzra's in the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而我在报社办公室里\NAnd I'm in the newspaper office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你手上的火药一擦就掉\NThat gunpowder will wash right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的手随我父亲\NI have my father's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拿着\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我给你拿条湿毛巾\NI'll get you a wet cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-给你  -没用的\N- Here. - It won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西德尼快失血致死了\NSidney's bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他需要医生\NNeeds a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他死掉更好\NHe needs to be put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就这么痛恨他吗\NYou that far gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样对谁都好\NIt's what's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}除了对露丝\NFor everybody but Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死  波汉南\NDamn it, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你去过墨西哥吗\NHey, you ever been to Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我靴子里有五美金\NI got $5 in my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要一把枪和一匹马\NI need a gun and a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可能需要两匹马\NMaybe two horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我才不管你有五美金还是五千美金\NI don't care if you've got $5,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}反正你会死在这里  被人开枪打死或者被绞死\NYou're gonna die in this town, by bullet or by rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这么难搞  我喜欢\NHard to get. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他怎么样了\NHow is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还没死呢\NHe ain't dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托\NOh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要的是医生  不是会舞文弄墨的\NI need a doctor, not some pencil dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给我听好  小混蛋\NListen to me, you little pissant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要想活过日落  我是你唯一的希望\NI am your only hope of surviving past sundown,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我建议你  不要惹毛我\Nso my advice is: Don't piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天啊\NGood God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是咖啡吗\NIs that coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}打仗的时候我们用那个来止血\NWe used it in the war to slow the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}难怪你们输了\NNo wonder you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}情况有多严重\NHow bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}子弹在下腹部\NBullet's lodged in the lower abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}划破了腹腔动脉\NIt's nicked the celiac artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果不把动脉缝合...\NIf I don't sew it up--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}止住血的话\NStop the bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他就死定了\Nhe won't need my help to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就治好他\NAll right, fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可不是魔术师\NI'm not a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}慢慢来吧\NLet's get started, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说了我撑不过去的\NI told you I wasn't gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行了吧西德  你也不是第一次中枪了\NOh, hell, Sid. You've been shot before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很多次呢  这是你自己说的\NPlenty a times, so you told it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是谎话\NI lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从没中过枪\NI ain't never been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}按住他\NHold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在努力\NI'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快点\NHurry -- hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找到了\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快取出来\NOkay, get it out. Get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊娃  给我拿个碟子来\NEva, get me a pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他了死吗\NHe dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还没\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看到了什么  露丝\NWhat did you see, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看到了什么  露丝\NWhat did you see, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起  爸爸\NI'm sorry, papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NI am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会再打你了\NI won't strike you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我你看到了什么\NTell me what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到了那些人\NI-I saw what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}出了什么事\Nto those men --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和你做的事\Nwhat you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是上帝的意愿  露丝\NIt's god's will, Ruth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为那些人是罪人\N'cause those men were sinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奴隶主\NSlavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在堪萨斯散播他们的邪恶\NPracticing that wickedness here in Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝需要通过我对这些人施以审判\NGod exacts judgment against such men through me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就是他手中的工具\Nthe instrument of his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是上帝的意愿\NIt's god's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝的意愿\NGod's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是什么\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝的意愿\NGod's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好孩子\NGood girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她不对劲\NShe's not herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在战争中你一定见过这样的场景吧\NI'm sure you've seen this in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喝水\NWater...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也冲不走嘴里那股金属味\Nwon't chase the metal from your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有金属味是因为心跳过快\NIt's from your heart racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是开枪杀人后的正常反应\NIt's what happens when you shoot a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的手也很凉\NAnd your hands get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这种感觉会过去的\NIt'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我杀了那个人\NI killed that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你谁也没杀\NYou ain't killed nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特把子弹从西德尼身上取出来了\NDurant dug the bullet out of Sidney.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在在为他缝合伤口\NHe's sewing him up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会为他犯下的罪受绞刑\NHe'll hang for what he done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们必须按法定程序来  博汉南先生\NWe will have due process, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}由你亲手执行  以你胸前警徽之名\NAnd by your hand, per that badge on your chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我们的约定\Nas we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她什么也没干\NShe ain't done nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}同样情况下你我也会做出一样的选择\NYou or I would have done if circumstances were similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要你拘留她  送她上法庭受审\NI want her jailed and arraigned before the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西德尼·斯诺才是该进监狱的人\NSidney Snow needs to be jailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只要他身体允许  他就会因谋杀罪受审\NSoon as he's able, he'll stand trial for murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}被定罪  绞死  然后被人遗忘\Nbe convicted, hanged, and forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但如果这之前他就死了\NIn the event he dies first,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那她就得负责\Nit must be seen that she's held accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为向西德尼·斯诺开枪拘留教会的女士\NYou arrest the church lady for shooting Sidney Snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恐怕你这临时州长也就当不下去了\Nthat might be your last act as provisional anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她对你就这么重要吗\NShe means that much to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对整个镇子都很重要\NWhole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}派个守卫看着她  剩下就看上天的安排了\NPost a guard 'til we see what providence brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}终点站到了  夏安站\NEnd of the line folks! Cheyenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最后一站  终点站啦\NLast stop! End of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果是你是来找麻烦的  你最好赶紧走\NIf it's trouble you bring, you best keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}里面有我们有很多人\NWe got our fill within.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是专门解决麻烦的  夫人\NTrouble's what I seek, madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比如迈克尔·麦克吉尼斯这样的\NIn the form of Michael Mcginnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道哪里能见到他吗\NWould you happen to know where I might encounter him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说他离开镇子了\NI heard he left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那么\NWell, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果是他亲爱的表兄想见他呢\NSuppose it's his dear ol' cousin who'd be asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你见过他吗\NWould you have seen him then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就算是耶稣本人来问我\NI don't care if it's Christ himself asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也没见过麦克吉尼斯  也不想见他\NI haven't seen Mcginnes and I don't expect to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是个火爆的俏娘们  对吗\NYou're a fine bit of stuff, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们去妓院找吧\NThe brothel, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不是西部走廊\NWell, if it isn't the ugliest mug
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个奇丑无比的人吗\Nwest of the bleeding channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-约翰尼  -迈克尔\N- Johnny! - Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}见鬼  你好吗\NHow the hell are ya? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}饥饿  饥渴  想打架\NHungry, horny, itching to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你一点都没变\NYou haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以为你不会来了\NBeginning to wonder you wouldn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}纽约和这里相隔遥远\NAh, miles of cathouses and saloons
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}路上有很多妓院和酒馆  迈克尔\Nbetween New York and here, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但这里是最好的  伙计\NBut none as fine as this establishment, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}女士们  这是我表兄  "阔少"约翰尼·舍伊\NLadies! This is me cousin, "Dandy" Johnny Shea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这群罕见的保加利亚人是"死兔帮"成员\NAnd this pack of rare Bulgarians are the dead rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"死兔帮"一般是爱尔兰和意大利移民的暴力帮派
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}欢迎  伙计们\NWelcome, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}欢迎  我说\NWelcome. Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们为什么不带他们上楼\NWhy don't you take them upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好好欢迎一下他们来到夏安\Nand welcome them to Cheyenne properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-来吧  -好的先生\N- Let's go. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快  起来  我要跟我表弟聊聊\NGo on, get up. I'll speak to me cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真俏\NHell yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迈克尔\NSo, uh, Michael.
