Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有时候\Nsometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当他离开家里\NWhen he left home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}开始致力于为印第安人发声\Nto speak for the Indians once and for good,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我读了描写他功绩的每一篇报道\NI read every article on his exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们称他为殉道者\NAnd they called him a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是个殉道者\NI'm not a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是怎么看自己的\NHow do you see yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是个母亲\NI'm a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这会疼死你的\NThis is going to hurt like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不不不  不要  等等  等等\NNo no no no! No! Wait wait wait wait wait wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}动手吧  博汉南\NNow, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-求你了  伙计  -别动\N- Come on, man. - Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样会快一点\NIt'll go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别把它切下来\NDon't cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.05,0:25:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}向你致以我的哀悼  露丝小姐\NMy condolences, Miss Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了以斯拉的离世\NOver Ezra passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你  帕萨姆\NThank you, Psalms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.41,0:25:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你需要什么吗\NWhat you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去帮您拿\NI'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.89,0:25:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不了  我只需要过去\NNo, I need to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在这里就是为了确保你留在原地\NI-I'm here to see you stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是博汉南先生的命令\NMr. Bohannon's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.40,0:25:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你能告诉我斯诺先生的情况吗\NWell, can you tell me what's happening with Mr. Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说博汉南先生在尽自己所能  救他一命\NI hear Mr. Bohannon doing everything he can to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.82,0:25:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救他一命\NSave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么救\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了救你  露丝小姐\NTo save you, Miss Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.26,0:26:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得你最好还是进屋去\NI think it's best you go back inside, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.16,0:26:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}假如有一天我躺上了那张桌子\NIf I'm ever on that table,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.35,0:26:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望你在身边\Nwant you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}假如你真躺上了那张桌子\NIf you're ever on that table,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.03,0:26:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望是我把你弄上去的\NI hope I'm the one puts you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.51,0:26:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}棺材里的不是埃兰\NIt wasn't Elam in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你自己说的\NYou said so yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.02,0:26:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃兰想要我\NElam wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.97,0:26:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他本可以和我一起和平离开的\NHe would have left quiet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.40,0:26:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而你夺走了这一切\NAnd you took that from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.86,0:26:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊娃...\NEva...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.88,0:26:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是为了保护你\NIt was for your own protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.07,0:26:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没人求你保护我\NNo one asked you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.16,0:27:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恭喜\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.62,0:27:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没死\NYou ain't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.03,0:27:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这一切都是为了看我被绞死吗\NAll this to see me hang?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.93,0:27:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.76,0:27:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}首先  你要救下教会的女士\NFirst you gonna save the church lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.28,0:27:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个善举不能洗净我所犯下的一切罪恶\NOne good act ain't gonna wash away all the bad I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.45,0:27:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这种人会变成什么样呢  博汉南\NWhat becomes of men like us, Bohannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.14,0:27:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得我们的结局会如何\NWhere do you suppose we end up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.92,0:27:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会好\NNowheres good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个混蛋会活下去吗\NThat bastard gonna live?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.79,0:27:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把他的腿锯掉了\NTook off his damn leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那他会比以前更恶毒的\NHe gonna be meaner than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.25,0:28:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恶毒不了多久了\NNot for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.79,0:28:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你安排了守卫看着我\NYou posted a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.90,0:28:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们把他的腿锯下来了\NWe took the leg off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.81,0:28:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会活下去的\NHe'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会为以斯拉的事受到惩罚的  露丝\NHe will answer for Ezra, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我会为伤害他而受到惩罚吗\NBut will I answer for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会被释放的\NYou'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.87,0:28:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会重建你的教堂\NWe'll rebuild your church.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.47,0:28:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们无法补救我所失去的东西\NYou can't rebuilt what I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.89,0:29:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你当外科医生可比我当农民强多了\NYou're a better surgeon than I was a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.24,0:29:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}根据我对你仅有的一点了解  这说明不了什么\NWell, from what little I know of you, that's not saying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.82,0:29:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以前想当个眼科医生\NI wanted to be an eye doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.78,0:29:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}研究眼科\NStudied ophthalmology.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我没有上完医学院\NBut I never finished medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.82,0:29:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道吗\NDid you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.73,0:29:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"大佬"[医生]这个称呼\N'Doc' is an affectation a--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.70,0:29:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只是我用来\NAn honorific title
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.96,0:29:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给自己在铁路这行提升地位的假头衔罢了\NI adopted to help me in the business of railroading.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.78,0:29:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你骗我的吧\NYou're shitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.89,0:29:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有\NI am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.85,0:29:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.66,0:29:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得像我们这样的人\NWhat you think is gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.29,0:29:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以后会有什么结局\Nhappen to men like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.17,0:29:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁路建成之后\NAfter she's built.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.38,0:29:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我将作为\NWell, I will be remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.37,0:29:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}建成越州铁路的人被人们铭记\Nas the man who built the transcontinental railroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.78,0:29:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但没人会记得你\NYou will not be remembered at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.96,0:30:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}连我都不会记得\NNot even by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.14,0:30:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感谢你如此直白\NThanks for sugarcoating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.27,0:30:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是真的\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你命够长  就会发现我所说都是对的\NYou live long enough, you'll see I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.51,0:30:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.47,0:30:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想在死前最后再看一眼这世界\NI thought I'd see the world one last time before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你走不远的\NWon't get far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.58,0:30:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天啊\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.53,0:30:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看过一个联邦军队的小子爬了半英里\NI saw this union boy once, crawl a half-mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.19,0:30:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}腰以下什么都没有\NNothing from the waist down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.46,0:30:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他最多17岁\NHe couldn't have been more than 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.94,0:30:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真是惨不忍睹\NIt's a hell of a sight to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.78,0:31:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有腿的家伙  匍匐前进\NA man with no legs, pulling himself along.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.25,0:31:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我追着他\NI chased him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.19,0:31:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到他实在爬不动了  我一脚踩在他身上\N'til he couldn't go no more and I pinned him with my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.72,0:31:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟他说  你急什么啊  小子\NSaid, "What's your hurry, boy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.76,0:31:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他开始翻他的外套\NHe started looking through his jacket right about then,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.87,0:31:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找一张照片\Nfor a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.39,0:31:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他想最后再看一次他的妈妈\NSee, he wanted to see his momma one last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在他临死前\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.95,0:31:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得他恨不得把外套弄穿\NI remember he dug all through that coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的很拼命地找\NHe looked real hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.77,0:31:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一直求我帮他找\NKept begging me to help him find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.90,0:31:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说  糟了  小子\NI said, "Well, hell, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.09,0:31:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}照片可能在你裤兜里呢\NThat picture's probably in your pants pocket."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.80,0:31:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我大笑了一通\NI had a good laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.58,0:32:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都有自己的牵挂\NWe all got moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.21,0:32:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我杀的每个人都有自己牵挂的某人\NEvery man I ever killed got one someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.77,0:32:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死  西德\NDamn, Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.39,0:32:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得去告诉教会的女士\NI need to tell that church lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.15,0:32:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从没打算伤害她的男孩\NI never meant to hurt her boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.04,0:32:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道我们这种人都是这种结局  博汉南\NI know it happens to men like us, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.39,0:32:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}死在离家千里之外的地方\NWe end up far from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.00,0:32:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}血肉模糊\Ncovered in blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.52,0:32:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狼狈不堪\Nand shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.37,0:32:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}孤独死去\NWe die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.32,0:32:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说闭上你的臭嘴\NI said shut your damn mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.97,0:32:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭上你的臭嘴\N"Shut your damn mouth."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有意思\NThat's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.37,0:33:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西德\NSid?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.59,0:34:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很开心\NThis pleases me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拥有一个珍视圣言的孩子\NThere's a--it is a blessing to have--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.13,0:34:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是一件幸福的事\Nto have a child who cherishes god's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.16,0:34:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真是我的好...\NYou are my good--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可爱的好女儿\Ngood and beloved daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.90,0:34:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"不可杀人"\N"Thou shalt not kill."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.52,0:34:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}昨晚那些人\NThose men last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是上帝派我惩罚他们所犯的罪孽\NGod sent me to them to, uh-- to avenge their sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.90,0:35:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"伸冤在我\N"'vengeance is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.06,0:35:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我必报应  主说"\NI will repay,' saith the lord."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.47,0:35:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  这是保罗对罗马人说的\NYeah. Paul to the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.84,0:35:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}撒旦有时也会引用圣经\NSatan himself does sometimes quote scripture.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.92,0:35:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是他最邪恶的伎俩之一\NIt's one of his foulest tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.92,0:35:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"不要自己伸冤\N"Avenge not yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}宁可让步  听凭主怒"\NBut rather give place unto wrath."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.12,0:35:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}够了\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.17,0:35:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些话是什么意思  爸爸\NWhat does it mean, papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.34,0:35:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等你长大了\NWhen you're older the--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.09,0:35:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真义自会揭示\NThe truth meanings will stand revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.92,0:35:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以主才让长老引导我们\NThat is why the lord puts our elders above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.67,0:36:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝\NRuth?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.78,0:36:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝不会通过他的造物复仇\NGod doesn't avenge sins through his creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.02,0:36:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不会让人杀人\NHe doesn't move men to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.76,0:36:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我见过的很多人\NI've met plenty of men who would
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.66,0:36:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都会颠覆你的这个想法\Nhave you believe differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.58,0:36:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不信赖上帝\NYou don't rely on god...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.24,0:36:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对吗  埃里森小姐\NDo you, Miss Ellison?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.07,0:36:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.79,0:36:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.84,0:36:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我见过很多人以主之名犯下恶行\NI've seen far too much of what men do in his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.33,0:36:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我难以相信上帝真的存在\Nto believe that he would ever be there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.76,0:37:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃里森小姐\NMiss Ellison.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定要走这步吗\NYou sure you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.34,0:37:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定要起诉露丝·科尔吗\NAre you sure you want to prosecute Ruth Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.27,0:37:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有了西德尼·斯诺这种人\NThe world is a better place
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.11,0:37:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个世界会变得更好\Nwithout men like Sidney Snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.80,0:37:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而科尔女士这样道德高尚的女人也会让世界更好\NAnd better with women of high moral standards like Miss Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.41,0:37:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以及你\NAnd yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}约翰  这不是回答\NJohn, that's not an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.99,0:37:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是官方口吻\NThat's a public position.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.65,0:37:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是傻瓜  路易丝\NI'm not a fool, Louise,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.55,0:38:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我是州长  这是有所意义的\NBut I am the governor and all that implies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.66,0:38:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我能引用这句话吗\NCan I quote you on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.89,0:38:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不能\NNo, you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.30,0:38:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}事实上\NIn fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我建议在此事尘埃落定前\NI would suggest that until this matter resolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.87,0:38:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不要在报纸上报道\NYou keep it out of the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.64,0:38:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是请求\NIs that a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.07,0:38:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还是威胁\NOr a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.92,0:38:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}公众的癔病可帮不了科尔女士\NPublic hysteria will not help Miss Cole's cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.10,0:38:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也帮不了你\NNor yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.00,0:38:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他这种人\NHe's better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.62,0:38:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}死了更好\NA man like that--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.73,0:38:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而我们这种人\NMen like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}仍然职责在身\NWe still got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.42,0:39:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道你的职责是什么\NYou know what yours is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.81,0:39:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去把淤泥马车驶过来\NI'll bring the muck wagon around.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.44,0:39:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是那个意思\NThat's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你是什么意思\NI know what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.37,0:39:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他死了  对吗\NHe's dead, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.09,0:41:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本周被杀者  以斯拉[姓氏未知]  西德尼·斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.56,0:41:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起  露丝\NI'm sorry, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.86,0:41:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这不是你的错\NIt wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.66,0:41:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也不是上帝的意愿\NOr god's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.44,0:41:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会想办法的\NI'll figure a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很好  博汉南先生\NI'm fine, Mr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.38,0:41:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}唯一一件比枪击斯诺先生更令我心满意足的事\NThe only thing more satisfying than shooting Mr. Snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.55,0:42:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是听到你告诉我他的死讯\NWas the moment you told me he was dead.

